Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsukikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:01:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Tsukikage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekka, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit! There's more of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You get out of here, Rekka.\NLeave this one to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'll live through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't have you die here along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, you get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsukikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you were to die here,\Nwho will then be able to stop them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsukikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekka!
