Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekka... Rekka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As the young leader\Nof the Crimson Lotus...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...your mission is to defeat the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crimson Lotus...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekka! Get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsukikage...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We, the Crimson Lotus, are an\Nanti-demon brigade formed under...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...the direct command of the\NShogun to destroy the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you were to die here, who will\Nthen be able to stop them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsukikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, so you're finally awoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, um... Where am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found you lying by the riverbank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure was tough\Ncarrying you back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here. You must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no poison in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll help myself to it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:03.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Old lady... Old lady...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:05:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I was just...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let go of her, you demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This village is the one that\NTsukikage and I were going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sex murders thought to\Nbe perpetrated by demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...have been taking place\Nin various parts recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to pin down what\Nthis mayhem was about...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...we were supposed to gather here with\Nthe other Crimson Lotus warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsukikage would've checked\Nout the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and would've been waiting for me\Nand the rest of our group.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those were my naive expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:33.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dare you come\Ncrawling over here like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not only did you abandon\NTsukikage to her death...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...but you even let a demon\Ntake the woman that saved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're being fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Rekka feels just as badly\Nabout Tsukikage as we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that. But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was nothing I could say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we were brought to the\NCrimson Lotus while we were kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...we were only taught how to fight,\Nwithout being told of our purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During those endless days of brutal\Ntraining we had to endure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...it was Tsukikage who supported us\Nand kept our morale up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The words of Akane and Ayano\Nwho suddenly appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...were biting into me along\Nwith my recent experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:24.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:26.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! When I was\Nwalking in the forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...it just suddenly appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ran away as fast as I could,\N'cause I thought I'd get eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet that's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet that's the one that\Nkidnapped my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much longer are you going to sulk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That might be the same woman\Nas the one that saved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. We might\Nstill make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:58.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the area that those\Nvillagers were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That cabin looks pretty\Nsuspicious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone must be out back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's just charge him\Nat once and be done with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be way too reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if he wasn't the one we're after?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll deal with that then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used to have friends\Nand such around, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...they were attacked\Nby the Black Steel one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Black Steel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I'm all alone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if I don't keep at it, no one will\Nbe there to protect the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to make up for\Nthe friends who were taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd say that we were\Nthinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he may be harmless to people...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...he's still a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we allow a demon\Nto live free like this out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't be sure he'll never reveal\Nhis true nature and attack people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only I didn't look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The people of the village are terrified\Nwhen they see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do I have horns like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think it would be better\Nif I always smiled like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not like the demons who\Nkidnap women from the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Do you know where\Nthose other demons are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's a bamboo\Nforest just a little further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They hang out in the\Ncave at the far end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come and see me sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, I'll serve up some tasty\Ndelights found in this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right. I'm sure we'll be by again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane, why didn't you kill that demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because he was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, he didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose you're right.\NEven if he is a demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...he's not an enemy of ours\Nunless he's out to harm people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We do want to avoid fighting any\Nunnecessary battles, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there are other demons that\Nwe should be going after anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How detestable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekka, that woman's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's from that cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:03.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekka, you have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can leave this to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel like... I feel like\NI'm going to burst...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to burst...!\NI'm going to burst...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is this woman who lies\Ncollapsed at my feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she weren't here\Nin this wretched scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that would be the face of any\Nordinary woman gently sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pondered her predicament.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Burdened by such a power\Nthat transforms her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...she lay secretly in waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beneath the innocence of\Nthis expression of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...what amount of darkness lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you're name is Haruka.\NIt must've been pretty rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you've got nowhere to go,\Nwhy don't you join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Rekka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, what's the matter with this dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane! You picked him up, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do something about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't she scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you attracted\Nto such a stinky place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:44.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ayano, could this dog be a male...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...or a female?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell by the way\Nthat stupid dog is behaving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dare you call him "stupid."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, now, have you already\Ngiven him a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Chiyomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiyomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a boring name that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just tried it out on him before.\NThat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiyomaru would be in\Nsuch bad taste, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, can you think of a better name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about "Whitey"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he's not white!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about something like "Bean"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? "Bean"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Not Mr. Bean.\NI mean, "bean" as in bean bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bean bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I love bean bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Doesn't seem quite right, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:41.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about we all call out\Na name at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and we'll make it the\Nname he responds to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that sounds like such fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, then. Let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:17:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Whitey.\N- Bean.\N- Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand the\Ntrouble we're going through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think Chiyomaru's about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:55.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just can't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:58.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell\Nthem about me before?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I'm not exactly normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't actually\Nunderstand it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What that power was,\Nor why I became like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be the ugly demon blood\Nthat courses through my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:27.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were organized as a\Nbrigade to fight the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I learned today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that not all demons are evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:36.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you fought against the demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...who captured all those innocent\Nwomen from the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need to get\Neveryone all upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I do kind of\Nowe my life to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:48.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Rekka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was asked if I\Nwanted to join you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I started feeling guilty\Nabout my true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been alone all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so happy until that day\Nwhen those demons showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They took everything away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My family, my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:16.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lost my parents as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or, perhaps I should say I\Ndon't even remember them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before you saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:31.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...there was one other\Nwoman who saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was younger...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:39.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I had lost my memory, and was\Napparently wandering the forests.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The leader of the Crimson Lotus then\Nfound me and adopted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:47.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had sword wounds all over my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was close to my last breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Tsukikage was there to nurse me\Nback to health every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, we did everything together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bathing together, eating together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She treated me as though\NI were truly her little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At times, even like her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It made my training with\NCrimson Lotus much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All because she was there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having lost my memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...she was the only one\Nwho made me feel at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You feel so strongly about Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From now on, I will be\Nthe one to protect you, Rekka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't let the demons get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Maybe I've said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you mustn't. You have Tsukikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just a...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:51.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mustn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mustn't be doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekka, you mustn't! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you really mustn't! I'm filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.71,0:22:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's demon blood in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.15,0:22:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dirty down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.69,0:22:45.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! It's dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.79,0:22:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:22:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.91,0:23:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really mustn't be doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.75,0:23:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a filthy body...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.49,0:23:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekka...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.59,0:23:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I'm not worthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:19.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right. You are just yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.37,0:23:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.16,0:23:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't take anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:23:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm going to go crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.13,0:24:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somethings not right.\NSomethings not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.07,0:24:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.08,0:24:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.85,0:24:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekka!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.62,0:24:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.62,0:24:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.95,0:24:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm hot all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.70,0:25:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going crazy! I'm going crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.67,0:25:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to cum!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.07,0:25:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.94,0:25:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to cum!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.82,0:25:29.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruka...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.13,0:25:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. What have I done.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.56,0:25:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.66,0:25:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's gone that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.60,0:25:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kill him, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.30,0:25:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.24,0:25:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's all the ruckus?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.07,0:25:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.28,0:25:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell? We just\Narrested one of them demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.25,0:25:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "arrested"?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.68,0:25:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just a lynch mob\Nattacking a defenseless creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.88,0:26:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.02,0:26:04.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd bring some of\Nthese to you guys, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.59,0:26:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I suppose I'm not supposed\Nto come to where humans live.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.57,0:26:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for causing all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.17,0:26:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.21,0:26:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going soft, Lotus.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.81,0:26:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Letting a demon off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.61,0:26:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.32,0:26:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.75,0:26:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Kagemai.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.62,0:26:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like the Crimson Lotus,\Nthose men also belong to a brigade...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.06,0:26:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...whose mission it is to hunt down\Nand capture demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.59,0:26:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are the Black Steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.16,0:26:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.79,0:26:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't blame you for\Nnot knowing about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.06,0:26:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike you...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.86,0:26:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...we are under the direct\Ncommand of the Great Elder.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.50,0:26:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although the Kagemai and\Nthe Crimson Lotus are charged with...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.14,0:26:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...with investigation and solving\Nincidents related to demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.04,0:26:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...the Black Steel are strictly\Nan assassin brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.48,0:27:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would say their fighting ability is\Nbeyond that of the Crimson Lotus.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.22,0:27:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.59,0:27:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will take this one with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.19,0:27:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.52,0:27:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is prey that we hunted down.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.96,0:27:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What we do to it has\Nnothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.60,0:27:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.60,0:27:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!